Let's install docker-compose

vagrant@u16vag:~$ sudo curl -L https://github.com/docker/compose/releases/download/1.21.0/docker-compose-$(uname -s)-$(uname -m) -o /usr/local/bin/docker-compose
  % Total    % Received % Xferd  Average Speed   Time    Time     Time  Current
                                 Dload  Upload   Total   Spent    Left  Speed

vagrant@u16vag:~$ sudo chmod +x /usr/local/bin/docker-compose
vagrant@u16vag:~$ docker-compose -v
docker-compose version 1.21.0, build 5920eb0


**************     VERY OK  !!! *************************************


